caption: <em>[type]</em>

Toggle uglifiers for specific tiddler types. Values for ''//[type]//'' include the following:

<ul><$list
	variable="type"
	filter="[all[uglifiers]]">
	<li>''<$text text=<<type>> />''</li>
</$list></ul>

These settings don't take effect until after a full refresh of either your tiddlywiki file or your Node.JS server.
